Package com.thebluealliance.api.v3.requests

Provides classes with the methods necessary to make requests to The Blue Alliance API.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    APIResponse
    Holds a response from The Blue Alliance API v3
    DataRequest
    Used to issue a direct request for data to The Blue Alliance via a URL
    DistrictRequest
    Makes requests with district-specific information
    EventRequest
    Makes requests with event-specific information
    MatchRequest
    Makes requests with match-specific information
    TeamRequest
    Makes requests with team-specific information
